{"tid":919963,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日搭巴士有一堆學生嘈山晒","createTime":"2018-11-28T12:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T08:00:07.000Z","uid":6122,"like":12,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"641b9d5a60cb9bec5b7ffd7049faef0b583b34fe","tid":919963,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日搭巴士返屋企<br />\n咁有班睇落大學生嘅人係好鬼嘈<br />\n本身都冇乜留意佢地<br />\n但佢地講嘢都幾大聲<br />\n我都冇心偷聽佢地講嘢<br />\n有個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就話：「你諗住做OC? OC冇嘢玩好悶㗎喎」<br />\n聽到呢度大概知道係班大學生<br />\n咁我就諗佢地一定係CU嘅人嚟（架巴士九龍塘附近開）<br />\n巴士上咁嘈真係影衰晒城大<br />\n直到佢地轉話題講起食開咩canteen<br />\n佢地竟然講medcan和聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再望一望佢地着嘅T<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先知佢地其實係中大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心讀中大就唔好講咁大聲啦<br />\n慌死人唔知佢地中大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為中大一份子我都有啲慚愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得前面有個女仔一直陰陰嘴笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個時候我都冇眼睇諗住插返耳機瞓覺算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知我唔小心跌咗張學生證出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （我放喺case裏面）<br />\n我已經即刻執起收返埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身都冇咩人見到<br />\n但後面突然有個男仔拍拍我膊頭話：「Hi 清你原來都係中大？我地都係呀 你咩書院㗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前面個女仔重望過嚟笑我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搵晒窿捐咁答返話：「我U...UC嘅...」<br />\n跟住佢地重大大聲擺晒手勢嗌：「UC~摺埋~~ UC~ 摺埋~~」<br />\n全車人聽到晒都喺度笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我拿拿臨撳鐘下個站轉第二架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n急急腳落車 隔離個師奶重提我攞返個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f827cd1f2b52ebed29a773f4299a58b4c54910","tid":919963,"uid":200834,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"164992588783922d1a19a3d2182abf0fac93a42c","tid":919963,"uid":204646,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"ok la,4/10"},{"pid":"484e5926edeb8f2b523068eff4537a4ae393906d","tid":919963,"uid":144401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:44:11.000Z","msg":"UC~摺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38fd0c4dfa406b0b11924cd3d51ad9364090d8c","tid":919963,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"召喚會員 uc褶埋"},{"pid":"6fe086446f3a01055ad1ebeaa95b66461822c0cf","tid":919963,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:45:26.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"eb13b65f4754037294d50460f3c6bc51ddc61dba","tid":919963,"uid":192491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"抵死啦 唔係禾含"},{"pid":"0d01e9d160e88ef1427127a93772826398c70293","tid":919963,"uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"we are shaw the best of all"},{"pid":"ec204307368844f99ed6ed0ba5557e82fdc2f4e6","tid":919963,"uid":138732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad4232faa864a7e281eb24c4f9374f6881a1eea","tid":919963,"uid":152520,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"有無即該dem返個中大econ beat比佢嘆？<br />\n外務黃敏力，唔知乜鳩佢嘅專長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616814b1c1d420000e92e87c978